title: A* Pathfinding Algorithm in python
author: DrCrossBones
text:
This project is a part of the larger scale project called [pathfinding into programming](https://reverend-toady.github.io/pathfinding-into-programming/) that I am undertaking to learn and document my journey in learning and exposing myself to as many languages as I can to pick my favourite one.

The plan is to make a Pathfinding Algorithm in each language that I try, in this case Python

You can find the python pathfinding repo [here](https://github.com/Reverend-Toady/pathfinding-python) 

The installation guide and the running guide are all present in the README in the github repository


Hope you have fun running the program!
